{"type": "article", "id": 35775, "title": "别惦记黑胶唱机，带上这个盒子就够了｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-12-19T23:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 24894, "name": "HCWD Studio"}, {"id": 35687, "name": "HYFEN"}, {"id": 35971, "name": "Alfalfa Studio"}, {"id": 35974, "name": "Snejana Hill Cosmetics"}, {"id": 35975, "name": "Suprematika"}, {"id": 7058, "name": "造作"}, {"id": 35969, "name": "Pink Donut"}, {"id": 35970, "name": "Nicholas Hanna"}, {"id": 35972, "name": "Alfalfa Esquer"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 132, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161219215440TU9OcPBgNSACYuMV.png", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>RokBlok by Pink Donut</h3><p>为了减轻播放黑胶唱片的门槛，让更多人能够感受到这种介质的魅力，许多设计师都进行过不少尝试。最近，美国的概念设计公司 <a href=\"http://rokblok.co/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pink Donut</a> 就用它研发的一块长方体重新定义了播放黑胶唱片这件事。这个名为 RokBlok 的设备是目前世界上最小的无线“播放器”——之所以要打上双引号，是因为它本身并不是扬声器，需要通过蓝牙让其他设备播放出音乐。设计团队也考虑到了 RokBlok 的重量问题，因而在底部选用了橡胶轮，确保重心不会停留在唱针上。即便不自带播放功能，优异的便携性仍能为它加分不少。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/pinkdonut/rokblok-a-new-spin-on-vinyl\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价为 79 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219215632B2FqMQKwcEOWzJH4.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.558824\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219215631iPWrmK7ph1EJeUAw.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561765\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219215631WbHEPkMIDgRq45z6.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219215632zablBsLxpA9fnVQG.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.595588\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>President Clock by Nicholas Hanna</h3><p>一个多月前，美国总统选举落下帷幕，面对不可测的未来，洛杉矶艺术家 <a href=\"http://nicholashanna.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nicholas Hanna</a> 设计了这款四年才会旋转一圈的 President 石英挂钟。钟的内部采用了团队特制的芯片，仅使用一根指针。四年的时间让人难以察觉它的移动，再加上钟面并没有额外的符号，更让人感受到时间的漫长。制作团队也特意针对耗能进行了改良，据称它仅靠附赠的单节五号电池就能运转大约五年的时间。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/nicholashanna/the-president-clock-0\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价为 79 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219215659t7Can2dvWQl1Nizk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667045\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219215700LK0u7Y2a5r8eDoZs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667045\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016121921570087pJ2GfkSPFOzATU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667045\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612192157001qfbirFGIp6ezKXY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667045\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Reindeer Decoration by Z-Inhouse</h3><p>马上就是圣诞节了，相关的主题摆设总是能一下子烘托出节日气氛。这款驯鹿实木摆件由<a href=\"http://zaozuo.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">造作</a>出品，既可以作为装饰物，还能用来当首饰架。木质鹿身的形状并不复杂，圆润的体态本身就憨态可掬，圆钢制成的对称鹿角和鹿腿则延续了这种优雅简洁的风格，给人一种敦实温暖的感觉。这是它的<a href=\"http://zaozuo.com/item/300175\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 227 元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220120811uMkBNe803nIUgYyx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562530\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220120811WKCnIklmAyvSc30i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219215838wnMhtqZY3f1mGxNR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219215835rDyaBq9ucn3PhjlL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219215836hiXLWNywqGZgpCFn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Clover by HCWD Studio</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>我们熟悉的开瓶器似乎并没有什么强烈的存在感：除了在开酒瓶时露面之外，这件小工具往往被放在角落里。不久前，美国的 <a href=\"http://www.hcwangdesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">HCWD</a> 工作室就推出了一个多功能的开瓶器 Clover。这个用不锈钢制成的迷你圆柱体上端有两个对称的圆孔，既可以用来悬挂在厨房中，也可以将项链穿过，把它当作一个挂坠。这是它的<a href=\"http://thehyfen.com/clover-bottle-opener/clover\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 38 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219221432rvDpEPhbCXBO2M9x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.597059\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219221432dUHG1goRvTSF6Ki9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219221432CRPVXYmJUoNSTGHb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219221436HCql2Xp5rzFLe93n.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Iconic New York Illuminated by Alfalfa Studio</h3><p>美国设计工作室 <a href=\"http://alfalfastudio.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alfalfa Studio</a> 的创始人和创意总监 Alfalfa Esquer 已经在曼哈顿生活了 20 年，但他依然记得在纽约的第一个夜晚：当时还是个大学生的他被绚烂的灯光深深吸引，因此下定了要在这座城市居住的决心。继 2013 年推出 <a href=\"http://alfalfastudio.com/projects/iconic-new-york-the-best-new-york-souvenir/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Iconic New York</a> 地图海报之后，Esquer 又以自己着迷的夜景为主题，在已有的元素上做了一番更新。这款“夜景版”海报共包含 600 多个图标，比原版多了近 200 个。除了地标建筑之外，组织机构、名人、能够代表纽约文化的物品等都散落在海报上，让人有一种迷失纽约的感觉。海报的规格也颇为豪华，采用丝绒质感的黑色防皱纸制成。你可以通过<a href=\"http://alfalfanewyork.com/#!/Iconic-New-York-Illuminated%C2%A9/c/21293007/offset=0&amp;sort=normal\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买，售价为 175 美元，Esquer 的签名版售价 200 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219224433wyHIiQDVc50PWsBF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.528117\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219224432cgJB3YKmNjhSQetU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612192244338l50AHOeywzLuGqk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219224435CH0pyr74jafTcDSs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Snejana Hill Cosmetics by Suprematika</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>为了强调自然和有机的概念，俄罗斯创意机构 <a href=\"http://suprematika.ru/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Suprematika</a> 为护肤品牌 Snejana Hill Cosmetics 旗下的两条产品线设计了充满艺术元素的朴实包装。点缀了 Inspired by nature 系列的，是一个个与自然相关的黑色图案，看上去像是用木炭随性涂抹的创作，表现出这一产品线均采用手工制作的特点。另一条产品线名为 Inspired by Kyoto，设计师们分别在两个圆圈中用寥寥几笔呈现出富士山的景色，这种不够完整的图像刚好可以激发顾客的想象力和好奇心。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219225407faGgYqjRUNeiCd0c.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219225405F8kloivdzNK35yBe.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219225406MhgF19NSDbLdEP78.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219225406VOyWBgMD6XT1K7no.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161219225405lH5DGQWR6zUqMNcY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600151\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612192254060qsdGiRTy2ax8pKe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600151\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}